Welcome to Ballywole! Widely regarded as one of Ireland’s most charming villages, Ballywole is a wonderful place to visit, live and work in. It is one of the most picturesque, popular and historic towns in Ireland brim full of history, heritage, and world class hospitality.. Visitors to Kinsale are captivated by its beautiful setting; its long waterfront, yacht-filled harbour, narrow winding streets and brightly painted galleries, shops and houses. We are all very proud of our vibrant ‘little’ town and the incredibly beautiful surrounding countryside.
